It's a very good layout on the sports and simple and quick and very clear to see everything. and they are constantly improving the site, this year alone they have made cash out for horses and now they are doing live simulation in betting so you see the probability of your selection if it has a chance. And also very fast quick replying from administration if you need a quick reply and also if you win your cash goes in quickly. There was one thing that I would say that sky bet could do in the future is give a courtesy win . What I mean there was a horse miles clear of the field at the jumps and cleared the last but the jockey slipped off the saddle that day alot of bookie's still paid out the unfortunate event as it was like 10 yard's from the line. But they give your money back if there is an unseat at the start. I ament getting paid by them to advertise them I'm saying this because I believe they'll be the best in a few years to come as they are constantly improving their site.
